Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Hyde Park
Description: Serene park in the middle of London. A beautiful destinationn contrasting the busy London City. A nice break when walking around all day.

Name: St. Lucia
Description: My family visited when I was much younger. I loved it here- I learned to snorkel, and it was the most tropical place I had ever been.

Name: Cabo
Description: I went here last year on vacation with family friends. Decided on this trip I wanted to get Scuba certified when I got back - I did.

Name: Flathead Lake
Description: The clearest lake I have ever seen. I want to eventaully buy a house on Flathead Lake - the views are breathtaking.

Name: Salisbury Cathedral
Description: I was born in Salisbury and the Cathedral Lawn is a common place that people would go for picnics on warmer days - I spent a lot of time here.
